      "title": "Out of control: Family therapy and domestic disorder",
      "abstract": "PART ONE: THEMES AND SETTINGS The Troubled Home The Settings PART TWO: WESTSIDE HOUSE Discerning Domestic Authority Constructing the System Restoring Hierarchy PART THREE: FAIRVIEW HOSPITAL Domestic Sentiments and Control The Rationalization of Feelings Facilitating Expression PART FOUR: THE SOCIAL CONSTRUCTION OF DOMESTIC DISORDER Voice and Method Language and Domestic Reality"
